# BMI Calculator (C++)

A simple Body Mass Index (BMI) calculator written in C++.  
This program asks for your weight (kg) and height (meters), calculates your BMI, and shows your BMI category.

---

# BMI Categories

- Underweight: BMI < 18.5  
- Normal: 18.5 – 24.9  
- Overweight: 25 – 29.9  
- Obese: ≥ 30  

---

# Features

- Calculates BMI using the formula: BMI = weight / (height * height)
- Input validation for positive numbers  
- Displays BMI with category  
- User-friendly prompts and messages  

